quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  42,45,"A tinay …ďe kadi, hi…ďe wee…ďitee e magge, hara hi…ďe yankinii koyeera on, hi…ďe ndaarira ndaar…óe leppagol. Gom…óim…ďe …ďen wi'aya: \"Ko woni hayru …ďe …ďen, ko …ďen hayrim…ďe ko'e mun e …ďeynguureeji ma…ď…ďe …óin √Ďalnde Darngal\". Anndee pellet, too√Īu…ďe …ďen no e lepte duumii…óe"
  42,46,"Yi…ó…ďe alanaa …ďe, ko wallitoo …ďe, hara wanaa Allah. Kala non mo Allah majjini, haray laawol alanaa mo"
  42,47,"Nootee Joomi mon, ado √Īalaande arde, nde ruttoowo alaa …óum ka Allah. Nden √Īalnde, faaborde alanaa on, yeddugol kadi alanaa on"
  42,48,"Si …ďe …óuurnike non, haray Men nuliraali ma, aynoowo …ďe: fawaaki ma, si wanaa yottingol. Si wonii Men mee…óiniri ne…ó…óanke on neema immorde e Amen, o wewlira mo; si ko bone non he…ďi …ďe, sabu kon ko juu…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen ardiniri, a taway pellet, ne…ó…óo on ko jeddu…óo sanne"
  42,49,"Ko Allah woodani laamagol kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin. Himo taga ko O muuyi. Himo ye…óa mo O muuyani …ďi…ó…ďe rew…ďe, O ye…óa kadi mo O muuyani …ďi…ó…ďe wor…ďe"
  42,50,"maa O jillira …ďe wor…ďe e rew…ďe; Himo wa…óa dimaro, on mo O muuyani. Pellet, ko O Anndu…óo, Ha…ótan…óo"
  42,51,"Sellantaa ne…ó…óanke, nde Allah yewtata mo, si wanaa wahayu, maa e …ďaawo heedo, maa O immina Nulaa…óo (Malaa'ikaajo), on wayahina e duŇčayee(sakkitoore) Makko, kon ko O haaji. Pellet, ko O Toowu…óo, √Ďee√Īu…óo"
